talking with Sam S.E.M., and we pronounce it Suter, S-U-T-T-E-R, at the University of Chicago, and we're in the Ludwig, L-U-D-W-I-G, Rosenberger, R-O-S-E, and V-E-R-G-E-R, Library of Judaica.

